rows.label: qst003301_msg0001
rows.name: Mo-mo-mo? What is it, mo?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0002
rows.name: Illegal squatting!? Shatoto?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0003
rows.name:
Nobody was living here, mo...
Shatoto had no money for an inn,
so I just took a little nap, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0004
rows.name:
Besides, when Shatoto came to town,
a soldier told me to pay money, so
it's not illegal squatting, mo!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0005
rows.name:
Huh? Huh? Why do you
look so surprised, mo?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0006
rows.name:
Momo?! You don't need to pay
money to enter the city, mo?!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0007
rows.name:
Shatoto was tricked, mo...
Shatoto's allowance...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0008
rows.name:
Shatoto came to Gula to eat a
dish I've always dreamed of...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0009
rows.name:
I can't say I couldn't eat it with
the allowance my mom gave me, mo...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0010
rows.name: Mom, I'm sorry, mo...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0011
rows.name:
Mo? You'll get Shatoto
my dream dish, mo?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0012
rows.name: Yay! Yay, mo! I'm so happy, mo!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0013
rows.name:
You see, when I was little, a man
named Ahato came to Avaritia, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0014
rows.name:
He took a liking to Chanopon, the
famous dish of Avaritia, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0015
rows.name:
He said he'd make a Torigo-style
version of Chanopon someday, and
I came to Torigo to eat it, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0016
rows.name:
Shatoto has grown up, so I
wonder if he's made it and
is selling it now, mo?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0017
rows.name:
I don't have money to pay
for Chanopon, so I haven't
been able to look yet, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0018
rows.name:
Once Shatoto eats Ahato's Chanopon,
I'll leave here right away, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0019
rows.name:
You're the first kind
people I've met, mo. The
soldiers were scary, mo...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0101
rows.name:
Avaritia's Chanopon, Torigo style...
I wonder what it tastes like, mo?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0102
rows.name:
Shatoto has never eaten
anything from Torigo, so
I can only imagine, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0103
rows.name: *rumble*

rows.label: qst003301_msg0201
rows.name:
My tummy's rumbling... n-mo?
Something smells good, mo!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0202
rows.name:
Chanopon Ruska Noodles?
The Torigo-style Chanopon
made by that Ahato guy!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0203
rows.name:
It doesn't look anything like
the one in Avaritia, but...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0204
rows.name: Time to dig in, mo!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0205
rows.name:
*slurp* *huff*! *slurp*
*munch munch*...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0206
rows.name: Phew...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0207
rows.name:
The spicy soup clings to
the springy noodles and
plentiful vegetables...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0208
rows.name:
The Chanopon from Avaritia
has evolved in Torigo, mo!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0209
rows.name:
That was delicious, mo! Thanks
for the meal, mo! Ahhh...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0210
rows.name:
Thank you, mo. It's a
wonderful memory, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0211
rows.name:
I'll work hard to earn money so I can
bring my mom here to eat it, mo.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0212
rows.name:
Sorry for napping here, mo!
I'm going home now, mo!
